Okweyongera kw'obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe (COVID-19) mu European Union/Eggwanga ly'Eby'enfuna ery'e Bulaaya ne United Kingdom wakati wa January 1 ne March 15, 2020
Omutindo gw'abantu abalwadde ba coronavirus (COVID-19) guli mu nsi eziri mu European Union/European Economic Area ne mu United Kingdom, nga kino kikakasa nti wadde nga bali mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikulaakulana mangu mu mawanga gonna.
Okusinziira ku byemanyiddwa mu Italy, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'abasawo abakeberebwa ennyo balina okweteekerateekera abantu abalwadde ba COVID-19 abeetaaga obujjanjabi, naddala mu bifo eby'enjawulo.
Nga 31 Ddesemba 2019, omusujja gw'obubonero ogutamanyiddwa ensibuko gwabanga mu Wuhan, Hubei, China.
Ku Jjanwali 9, 2020, Ekitongole ky'Okukugira n'Okukuma Endwadde mu China kyagamba nti ekirwadde kino kyava ku kawuka ka coronavirus akaali keeyitibwa SARS-CoV-2.
Okuva olwo, obulwadde obuva ku kawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 buyitibwa obulwadde bwa coronavirus (COVID-19).
Mu kiseera kino, abantu nga 80 ku buli 100 abalina COVID-19 balina obulwadde obutonotono, kwe kugamba, obulwadde bw'omu bbanga n'obutaba na bulwadde bwa bwaki, era abasinga obungi bawona.
Mu bantu 14 ku buli kikumi, COVID-19 ebaleetera obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaagisa okuteekebwa mu ddwaliro, ate abantu 6 ku buli kikumi beeyongedde okufuna obulwadde obw'amaanyi obwetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro.
Omutindo gw'abantu abafa nga bakwatiddwa COVID-19 ku ddwaliro gwawera 4%.
Mu kunoonyereza kuno, twekenneenyezza okukyuka kw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga erya European Union/European Economic Area (EU/EEA) ne United Kingdom (UK), era ne tugeraageranya n'okukyuka okwaliwo mu ssaza ly'e Hubei mu China.
Tugeraageranya omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK n'omuwendo gw'abaali mu Italy okuva nga 31 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 March 2020.
Embeera ya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Oluvannyuma lw'e China, COVID-19 yeeyongedde okusaasaana, era embeera ya COVID-19 mu nsi yonna egoberera eya China.
Nga 11, Maaki 2020, dayirekita omukulu owa World Health Organization (WHO) yategeeza nti COVID-19 yali kawumpuli.
Mu magazini ya Eurosurveillance eya Maaki 5, 2020, Spiteri n'abalala baategeeza ku bantu abaasooka okukakasibwa okuba n'ekirwadde kya COVID-19 mu Bulaaya nga bwe kiragibwa mu kitongole kya WHO.
Mu EU/EEA, abalwadde abasatu abaasooka baakakasibwa nga bafukibwa Bufalansa nga 24 Jjanwali 2020 mu bantu abaava e Wuhan mu ssaza lya Hubei, China.
Nga 15 Maaki 2020, obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bwali bumaze okweyolebwa mu mawanga 30 aga EU/EEA ne mu Bungereza (UK) nga mu kiseera eky'omulundi 31 omwezi gwa Ddesemba 2019 abalwadde 39,768 n'abafa 1,727 be baawandiikiddwa, nga 17,750 ku bo baali balwadde ne 1,441 be baafiira mu Italy yokka.
Okufuna omuwendo gw'abantu abafunye obulwadde bwa COVID-19 n'engeri gye bajjamu
Mu kitongole ky'Ebulaaya eky'okutangira endwadde (ECDC), omuwendo gw'abantu abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu buli ggwanga mu nsi yonna, oguva mu bifo eby'obwannannyini nga minisitule y'ebyobulamu, ebitongole by'ebyobulamu mu nsi n'ebitundu n'ekitongole kya WHO, guzuulibwa buli lunaku ku ssaawa 8:00 ez'ekiro.
Ebintu bino byakozesebwa mu kuddamu okutunuulira COVID-19 mu EU/EEA ne UK, n'okugeraageranya n'ebyo ebibaddewo mu Italy.
Okusobola okumanya omuwendo gw'abantu abalina COVID-19, twabalirira omuwendo gw'abantu abaalina COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 okuva nga 1 Jjanwali okutuuka nga 15 Maaki 2020.
Era twageraageranya omuwendo gw'abantu abaakakasibwa mu buli ggwanga nga 15 March 2020 ku 8:00 a.m. n'ogw'abantu abaakakasibwa mu Italy okuva nga 31 January okutuuka nga 15 March 2020.
Enkulaakulana ya COVID-19 mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK
Enkyukakyuka mu bungi bw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 mu nsi za EU/EEA ne UK mu nnaku 14 zaagoberera eya Hubei mu China (Ekifaananyi 1).
Mu EU/EEA ne UK, COVID-19 yatandika okusaasaana ku Lwokubiri nga 21 Febwali era n'eyongera mu bwangu nga 28 Febwali 2020 (Ebisingawo).
Enkyukakyuka eno yava ku kudduka kw'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakosebwa obulwadde mu Italy, naye n'amawanga amalala gonna agali mu EU/EEAA ne Bungereza nago gaalaba okwongera kw'omuwendo gw'abantu abaakosebwa obulwadde bwa COVID-19 (mbalirira).
Ekifaananyi 2 kiraga omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa obulwadde bwa COVID-19 mu mawanga g'omu EU/EEA ne Bungereza nga gukuusa ku bya Italy okuva nga 31 Ogwokubiri okutuuka nga 15 Ogwokusatu 2020.
Kizuuliddwa nti, nga 8 00 ku 15 Ogwokusatu, amawanga amalala 15 mu EU/EEA ne UK gaali galaga obubenje obwenkanankana n'obw'e Italy wiiki ssatu ezaali emabega oba obutono.
Ebyazuuliddwa biraga nti omuwendo gw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 gweyongedde mangu mu EU/EEA ne UK.
Enkyukakyuka mu bungi bw'abantu abafa COVID-19 eraga nti endwadde eno yeeyongedde mu sipiidi y'emu mu mawanga gonna.
Kino kikolebwa wadde nga waliwo enjawulo mu nsi ez'enjawulo era nga waliwo enjawulo mu nzirukanya z'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu mu nsi, enjawulo mu ngeri abantu gye bategeeramu obulwadde era n'enjawulo mu nkola y'okulonda abalwadde okwekebejjebwa okukakasa nti balina COVID-19, nga mw'otwalidde n'okwekebera okudda mu mbeera.
Ku ntandikwa ya Maaki 2020, abasawo mu bitundu bya Italy ebirwadde bya COVID-19 baategeezezza nti abalwadde nga 10 ku buli 100 beetaaga okujjanjabibwa mu ddwaliro eririmu abalwadde ab'amaanyi, era amawulire gaafuluma nti amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'abasawo mu bitundu ebyo byali bituuse ku ntikko ya maanyi gaabyo.
Ebyafaayo ku COVID-19 mu malwaliro ne mu ICU mu kiseera kino bifunibwa mu EU/EEA ku 6% n'1% byokka eby'abantu abafunye obulwadde (ebitaalabikiddwa).
Kyokka, kyetaagisa okukuŋŋaanya obujulizi obugenda mu maaso okusobola okwongera ku bubonero obuliwo obwesigamye ku muwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa n'abafudde.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 201011 kwalaga enjawulo ya maanyi mu muwendo gw'ebisenge ebiriwo mu bifo by'obujjanjabi mu Bulaaya, okuva ku 29.2 mu Bugirimaani buli bantu 100,000 okutuuka ku 4.2 mu Portugal.
Kino kitegeeza nti amawanga galina ensimbi ezisinga oba entono ku ezo eziri mu Italy (12.5 mu buli bantu 100,000 mu 2010).11
Embeera ez'ekikugu ezikwata ku bujjanjabi obujjudde, nga ziteeberezebwa mu buli ggwanga mu EU/EEA ne UK ku bungi bw'abantu abajjanjabwa mu malwaliro olw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19 n'obuli ku bantu 90 ku buli 100 abali mu bifo eby'okulabirirwa eby'amaanyi, ziweereddwa mu kiwandiiko ekya CEPCM COVID-19 Rapid Risk Assessment eky'omukaaga.
Olw'okuba mu kiseera kino, abalwadde baakuŋŋaanyizibwa wamu mu bitundu ebimu mu mawanga ga EU/EEA ne UK, era nga n'amalwaliro n'ebitongole by'abasawo abakulu mu ddwaliro batera okwetegereza abantu ab'omu kitundu ekimu, ebiwandiiko ebikwata ku balwadde n'ebitanda mu ddwaliro ly'abakulu mu ddwaliro erya nnaddala byandibadde biteekebwa ku mutendera gwa 2 mu Nnyaza ey'ebitundu eby'ebbalirirwamu (NUTS 2).
Ebyafaayo bya Italy n'embeera eriwo mu nsi endala biraga nti ekirwadde kya COVID-19 kikula mangu mu EU/EEA ne mu UK.
N'olwekyo, ensi, amalwaliro n'ebitongole ebirabirira abalwadde mu ddwaliro erya wansi birina okwetegekera embeera y'okusaasaana okw'amaanyi okwa SARS-CoV-2 mu bantu n'okw'abalwadde ba COVID-19 abetaaga okulabirirwa, naddala mu ddwaliro lya balwadde ab'amaanyi, nga bwe kyali mu bitundu bya Italy ebikosezeddwa.
Nga bwe kyalagiddwa mu kunoonyereza kwa CEPCM okw'ebbula amangu, enkola ey'amangu, ey'obunyiikivu era ey'obutonde bw'ebintu byonna nkulu nnyo mu kukyusa okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2, okuva ku ngeri y'okuziyiza okutuuka ku ngeri y'okukendeeza, kubanga okwongera amangu mu bungi bw'abalwadde kiyinza obutalekaawo abakola ku by'enkola n'amalwaliro ebiseera ebimala okutegeera, okukkiriza n'okukyusa enkola yaabwe singa tewali kyakolebwa.
Okwewunyiza okw'amangu era kulaga enteekateeka z'ebyobulamu ez'abantu bonna ezinaakozesebwa okukendeeza ku bulabe bw'ekirwadde kino.
Waliwo ekiseera kitono buli nsi mw'eyinza okwongera amaanyi mu kufuba okwekolera okusobola okukendeeza ku kusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV-2 n'okukendeeza ku bwetaavu bw'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu.
Singa ekyo tekikolebwa, embeera y'obulamu mu nsi endala eziri mu EU/EEA eyinza okuba nga yeeyongera mu nnaku oba mu wiiki ezijja.
Obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe 2019 (COVID-19), obuleetebwa akawuka ka ssenyiga omukambwe (SARS-CoV-2) kati bufiiridde abantu abasukka 3,000 era nga bulwadde buno buliko abantu abasukka 80,000 mu China ne mu nsi endala, era nga buviiriddeko abantu okubonaabona ennyo.
Okufaananako SARS-CoV, eyaleeta enkumi n'enkumi z'abantu abalwadde SARS mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 eyinza okuyisibwa ng'ekyavudde ku bbaafu era n'eviirako obubonero obufaanana ng'obwo okuyitira mu nkola y'emu.
Kyokka, COVID-19 si ya maanyi nnyo era tewabaawo bantu bangi bafa ng'akawuka ka SARS, naye ekwatagana nnyo n'akawuka kano, era ekwata nnyo abantu abakaddiye okusinga abato, era n'abasajja okusinga abakazi.
Mu kuddiŋŋana n'omuwendo gw'ebitabo ebikubibwa ku bulwadde buno obuggya, ekitundu kino kigezaako okuwaayo okwetegereza okw'amangu era okw'omunda ku nsonga eno ey'okunoonyereza eri mu maaso.
Tujja kwogera ku misingi gy'obulabe bw'obulwadde, obwavu, obuwuka, okuzuula, okujjanjaba, okwetegereza n'okutangira obulwadde.
Wadde nga waliwo ebibuuzo bingi ebirina okuddibwamu, tusuubira nti bye twekenneenyezza bijja kutuyamba okutegeera obulungi obulwadde buno era n'okubuggyawo.
