Kikulu okukiggumiza nti okusala mu ngeri ey'obulabe kiyinza okuleeta enkyukakyuka mu bukugu bw'omulembe gw'akawuka ka siriimu, oboolyawo nga kiva ku bizibu ebiba bifuniddwa mu kulonda, naddala ebikolebwa mu mubiri gw'omuntu.
Ekyokulabirako kwe kufiirwa ORF4 mu HCoV-229E, olw'okusaanuuka kwa nucleotide bbiri.
Mu kiseera ORF4 we yalabikira mu kawuka ka katonnyolo ne ka eŋŋamira akafaanana ne HCoV-229E, akawuka ka alpaca alpha-CoV kalina ekitundu kimu kyokka eky'obutundu bw'ekika kya nukeleotidi, ekiviirako ekitundu ky'obutundu okufuluma.
Mu ngeri y'emu, ekirwadde kya coronavirus eky'omusanvu kiyinza okuleetawo obuzibu obw'amaanyi mu bantu.
Abalwadde abatalina bubonero oba abalina obubonero obutonotono baalabikanga ng'ennyonyi ez'ekika kino zifunye obulwadde bwa CoVs, ekiraga nti CoVs n'ennyonyi ez'ekika kino zifaanagana.
Kyali kirabika nti ebikonde by'ebiramu by'ebirume byali byategeera bulungi ekika kya CoVs.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, obuzibu mu kusobozesa obulwadde okuwona mu mbeere bukendeeza nnyo ku ndwadde eziva ku CoV.
Ate era, obunkenke bw'obutoffaali bw'ekika kya ssennyiga mu bannyaffe buziyizibwa olw'okufuga obulungi ekitundu eky'omubiri ekirwanyisa obunkenke bw'ekika kya ssennyiga ekya NKG2/CD94 era n'olw'omuwendo omutono ennyo ogw'obutoffaali bw'ekika ekinene eky'ekika ekisooka.
Ate era, omutindo ogunene ogw'ebirungo by'omukka (RDO) oguva mu by'okusaasaanya ebikolebwa ebisibo mu misinde g'empologoma guyinza okuziyiza CoV okwongera okw'eka era ne gukwata "okusoma" okuyitira mu exoribonuclease, ekiyinza okuleeta obunkenke ne kiviirako obuwuka obusoosa okuva mu ndwadde nga buyingidde mu mugenyi omupya.
Ensigo za CoV ezisinga okuleeta endwadde ziyinza n'okufuuka nga zikwatagana, nga zifuna obumu ku butoffaali oba obutoffaali obuyamba omubiri okwekuba.
Mu ngeri y'emu, tekiri nti HCoVs ssatu ze zaalabikira mu myaka ebiri egiyise zaali za bulabe.
CoVs tezirina bulabe oba zireeta obubonero obutonotono mu bantu be zisangamu nga amatooke n'eŋŋamira.
Zisobola okwezaala obulungi nga tezizzaawo buziyiza bw'omubiri.
Wano we we tusanga ebyama mu kulabira abalwadde abatalina bubonero ne mu kumanya ekireeta endwadde ez'amaanyi mu bantu.
Obubonero obw'amaanyi businga kuva ku buziyivu bw'obw'omubiri n'obw'ekika kya ssayitokini; obuzibu bw'obw'omubiri bwe businga, obuvune bw'amawuggwe bwe businga okuba obw'amaanyi.
Wabula, mu bantu abatalina bubonero, obujjanjabi bw'omubiri tebukwatagana na CoV.
Enkola y'emu ey'okusaasaanya enkola y'omubiri eyinza okuba ey'omugaso mu kujjanjaba SARS-CoV-2.
Obusobozi bw'ebika by'ensiri obw'okwanukula interferon naddala mu bakiggala bukulu nnyo.
N'olwekyo, okugaba interferon ey'ekika I waakiri mu mitendera egy'olubereberye mu bulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 kisuubirwa okuba eky'omuganyulo.
Ate era, NLRP3 inflammasome tekyalikola mu mize.
Okusinziira ku ndowooza eno, okuziyiza ekirwadde kya NLRP3 ne MCC950 kiyinza okuba eky'omugaso mu kujjanjaba COVID-19.
Mu ngeri y'emu, SARS-CoV-2 yazuulibwa nga yeeyita mu ngeri y'emu nga SARS-CoV ne MERS-CoV.
Mu kiseera nga beta-CoV eya baton y'emu n'eya SARS-CoV ku mutindo gwa nucleotide gwa 95 ku buli kikumi, waliwo ne baton CoV ey'emu n'eya SARS-CoV-2 ku mutindo gwa nucleotide gwa 96 ku buli kikumi.
Wadde nga ebiwuka ebiyitibwa civets n'ebirala ebisangibwa mu butale byazuulibwa nga birina akawuka akafaanana ne SARS-CoV, tewali muntu wa SARS-CoV-2 ey'omu butonde eyeeyita nti ye yajja.
Mu kiseera kino, abantu bangi bakkirizza nti SARS-CoV-2 erina akawuka ka beta-CoVs.
Wadde nga waliwo ebibuuzo ebiragibwa, tewali bukakafu bulaga nti SARS-CoV-2 yatondebwa muntu, k'abe nga yali agiteesezza oba nga teyeeteeseteese.
CoV zazzeemu okwetabwako olw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Mu kiseera kino, ekirwadde kya CoV kiwandikawo ebitundu by'omubiri ebitafaanagana mu mubiri, nga mu ngeri y'emu nga bwe kiwandikawo enkola ya CoV ey'omubiri.
Mu ngeri y'emu, abantu bafunye obuzibu mu kukwataganya obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'obw'okusaanyaawo obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Olw'okuba SARS-CoV ekwata abantu nga bakwatagana n'ebinyonyi ebito mu butale, okuggala obutale n'okutta ebinyonyi ebito mu butale kyandikuumye obulwadde bwa SARS.
Mu ngeri y'emu, pangolin zirina okuggibwa ku butale bw'eby'emmere ebikyafu okusobola okwewala okusaasaanyizibwa endwadde ez'ekika kya zoono, olw'okuzuula ebika bingi eby'akabonero ka beta-CoV okuva mu pangolin nga bikwatagana n'akabonero ka SARS-CoV-2
Kyokka, mu kunoonyereza okujja, kijja kulagibwa obanga SARS-CoV-2 esobola okusasaana okuva ku nsolo n'ebisolo ebirala, era n'engeri gye kisobola okusasaana.
Ku luuyi olulala, MERS-CoV yabaddewo mu mpologoma okumala ekiseera kiwanvu.
Eŋŋamira ze nnyonyi enkulu era ze zisinga okuleetera abantu mu kitundu ekyo emmere, amata, amaliba, n'engoye.
Zinoera nnyo mu Buwalabu ne mu Afirika.
N'olwekyo, tekisoboka kutta buli ŋŋamira okusobola okuziyiza MERS, nga bwe kyali mu butale bw'ebisolo mu China okuziyiza okusaasaana kwa SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2.
Okusobola okukomya obulwadde bwa MERS obuzzeemu okusaasaana, waliwo engeri ey'okukozesa ey'obutonde yonna okuteekawo eddagala erigema MERS-CoV mu balongo, nga n'ebirala biwereddwa.
Olw'okuba tetusobola kumalawo buwuka buno, genotype empya ziyinza okujjawo ne zivaako endwadde.
Waliwo obuwuka bwa CoV obuva mu nsolo obuyitibwa zoonotic mu nsolo.
Okusingira ddala, CoVs ez'ekisolo, ezirina obusobozi obw'okusaanyaawo ebisolo.
Waliwo omukisa omungi eri CoVs ez'ekika ky'ebisolo okudda n'okwekutula, ne kiviirako CoVs empya ez'omulembe ez'okusasaana n'okuzikiriza abantu mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Enkola y'okulya ensolo ez'omu nsiko mu bitundu ebimu eby'omu China yandirekeddwaawo okukendeeza ku nkolagana etetaagibwa wakati w'abantu n'ensolo.
Olw'ebyava mu SARS, MERS ne COVID-19, enteekateeka ennungi ey'okwetegekera n'okuddamu ebirwadde byetaaga okukolebwa.
Mu butuufu, waliwo obwavu bungi ku nsi okumala ekiseera kiwanvu.
Basula mu bifo byabwe eby'obutonde okutuusa nga waliwo akakisa ak'okusaasaanya.
Wadde ng'ebika by'ennyonyi ez'omulembe birina ebintu bingi ebisobozesa enjala okusaasaanyizibwa, enkola y'abantu okubeerako n'ennyonyi ez'omulembe n'ebika by'ebika ebirala eyinza okukendeezebwa singa abantu bayigirizibwa obutagwa mu bantu.
Okwejjanjaba okw'ebisolo kwetaagisa okusobola okutegeera embeera y'ebisolo bya CoV n'ebisolo ebye bizinga, ekijja okuyamba okutangira okusasaana kw'ebisolo mu bantu n'okutangira endwadde ez'omu maaso.
Mu nkomerero, engeri esingayo obulungi abantu gye bayinza okutangira endwadde z'obutabowa bw'ensolo kwe kwewala ebifo ebirimu endwadde z'obutabowa bw'ensolo.
Ebikwata ku nsibuko ya SARS-CoV-2 mu nsolo tebinamanyiddwa mu bujjuvu.
Okusooka, singa ebikajjo biyinza okuyisa akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 ku bbebi, kyandibadde kirungi okumanya embeera ebikajjo n'ebibbebi mwe biyinza okubeera mu kifo kye kimu.
Ekyokubiri, singa enyonyi z'engatto zikola kinene mu kussa obulwadde ku bantu, kyetaagisa okumanya engeri abantu gye bakolagana n'enyonyi.
Ekyokusatu, singa ekisolo ekimu eky'okusatu kibeera nga kye kisinziirwako, engeri gye kikwataganamu n'ebika ebirala, omuli abantu, ebikajji n'ebikajji, tekinnategeerekeka bulungi.
Mu ngeri y'emu, ekirwadde kya SARS-CoV-2 kiyinza okubalukawo nga kiva ku buzibu bw'okusaanyaawo endwadde.
Ka kibe nga kibeera ku bbebi, ku nsolo oba ku nsolo endala, SARS-CoV-2 oba obuwuka obufaanana ng'obwo obuli mu nsi gye bubeera bulina okuzuulibwa.
Okunoonyereza okukolebwa mu biseera eby'omu maaso ku nsonga eno kujja kuyamba mu kutegeera ekkubo SARS-CoV-2 ly'eyinza okuyita mu nsolo era kujja kubaako kye kuyinza okukola ku kuziyiza n'okufuga COVID-19 mu bantu.
Enkola empya ey'okumanya ekirwadde kya COVID-19 ekikwatiddwa n'ekikakasiddwa yeetaagisa
Nga February 6, 2020, ttiimu yaffe yafulumya ekiragiro ekikwata ku kujjanjaba obulwadde bwa ssenyiga omukambwe 2019 (2019-nCoV) era ekiragiro kino kyali kyogera ku bye twayitamu era ne kiwa n'ebiteeso eby'okukozesa okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino mu nsi yonna.
Wabula, endwadde ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) yaakatandika, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kugenda kweyongera okusinziira ku biva mu kunoonyereza n'okumanya ebiva mu nkola ey'ekisawo; n'olwekyo, enkola y'okwekebejja n'okujjanjaba nayo yeeyongera okuggumizibwa.
Mu bbaluwa eno, twaddamu okuddibwamu ku mateeka gaffe era ne tuwaayo ebisaanyizo by'okunoonyereza ebipya ku  omuntu akwatibwako  n'oyo  akakasiddwa  okusinziira ku mateeka agaggya aga COVID-19 (enkyukakyuka ey'omusanvu) agafulumiziddwa Akakiiko k'Eby'obulamu mu ggwanga aka China.
Mu December 2019, ekirwadde kya coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) kyaleetawo kawukaale kati akayitibwa Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19), era akawuka kano kaatuumibwa Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Nga 11 Maaki 2020, WHO yayita COVID-19 nti ye kawumpuli.
Okusobola okulwanyisa obulwadde bwa SARS-CoV-2, ttiimu yaffe yakola amagezi agafulumira ku mutimbagano ku Military Medical Research nga Febwali 6, 2020.
Kyazuuliddwa nnyo okuva lwe kyafulumizibwa.
Kyokka, weetegereze nti COVID-19 mulwadde mupya, okumanya kwaffe n'okumanya kweyongedde mpolampola okusinziira ku ebyo ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okukolebwa n'obumanyirivu mu nkola y'ekisawo; n'olwekyo, enkola z'okuzuula n'okujjanjaba nazo ziteekebwako obuggya buli kiseera.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, ebiragiro ebikwata ku kujjanjaba COVID-19 ebyafulumizibwa akakiiko k'eby'obulamu mu China (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/) byafulumizibwa emirundi musanvu wakati wa 16 Jjanwali 2020 ne 3 Maaki 2020, ng'ebimu ku byawandiikibwa byabikubazibwa nnyo.
Nga ekiragiro kyaffe kifuniddemu okuddibwamu okuva eri Zhou et al, bano baaleetawo enkola entuufu ey'okugezesa okusinziira ku kunoonyereza kwabwe.
Omulimu gwabwe guleese obujulizi obupya ku kiragiro kyaffe era guli n'obuyambi bw'amaanyi eri obulwadde buno obw'ensi yonna.
Tusiima omulimu omukulu gwe bakola era tubeebaza.
Kyokka, emirimu gyabwe girina okuddaabirizibwa okusinziira ku bulagirizi obusuubirwa mu kukebera n'okujjanjaba COVID-19 (ekigezo eky'omusanvu) n'ebyafaayo ebivudde mu kunoonyereza okwakolebwa.
Okusinziira ku lupapula olw'omusanvu (3 Maaki 2020), okukakasa akawuka k'omusaayi kulina okusaanyibwa n'emu ku nsonga ez'ekyafaayo kya siriimu awamu n'ensonga bbiri ez'ebikolwa by'omusaayi okusobola okuzuula ekituufu, oba okulondawo ensonga ssatu ez'ebikolwa by'omusaayi nga tewaliwo byafaayo bya siriimu:
Ebyafaayo: (1) eby'obuggya ng'omuntu agenze mu kibuga Wuhan ne mu bitundu ebiriraanyeewo oba ng'ali mu bitundu ebirala mwe baalagira nti waliwo COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ez'emabega ng'obubonero tebulabise; (2) eby'obuggya ng'omuntu alina akawuka ka SARS-CoV-2 (nga alina akawuka ka nucleic acid); (3) eby'obuggya ng'omuntu alina omusujja oba ng'alina obubonero bw'okussa mu kibuga Wuhan oba mu bitundu ebiriraanyeewo oba mu bitundu ebirala mwe baalagira nti waliwo COVID-19 mu nnaku 14 ez'emabega ng'obubonero tebunnalabise; (4) eby'obuggya nga waliwo abantu abaalagiddwa nga balina obulwadde bwa COVID-19 (abalina omusujja oba obubonero bw'okussa mu mubiri obwalimu obulwadde bwa fever/fever mu masaza 2 mu kifo ekimu ng'amaka, essomero, essomero, ekizimbe, n'ebirala).
Obubonero bw'obulwadde: (1) omusujja n'obulabe bw'omukka; (2) ebifaananyi ebiraga obubonero bw'obulwadde bwa COVID-19; (3) omuwendo gw'ebisenge by'omusaayi omweru mu mubiri ebiraga omuwendo gw'ebisenge by'omusaayi ebirimu ebisaanidde, ebirimu ebirwadde oba ebirwadde okuva obubonero lwe bwatandika.
Okuzuula omuntu okukakasibwa kulina kwesigamizibwa ku muntu eyeekweka ng'alina obujulizi bwonna obw'ekika ky'endwadde oba obw'omusaayi: (1) okwekebeza PCR mu kiseera ekituufu nga kulaga nti alina obubonero bwa SARS-CoV-2 (2); okukebera ekika ky'akawuka ka siriimu kyonna nga kikwatagana n'obwo obuli obwa SARS-CoV-2; (3) okwekebeza obubonero bwa siriimu bw'ebiwuka bya IgM ne IgG ku SARS-CoV-2; oba okukyusa obubonero bw'ebiwuka bya SARS-CoV-2 okuva ku mubi okutuuka ku kirungi oba okwongera mu butundu bwa kirwadde mu kiseera eky'okuddamu okuva mu mbeera ey'obulabe emirundi egisoba mu nnya.
Tusobola okulaba nti okwekebeza PCR mu kiseera ekituufu ku asidi ya nukiriya mu nsawo oba mu bigezo by'omusaayi kwongerwako mu kiwandiiko eky'okubiri (Jjanwali 18, 2020) ne mu kiwandiiko eky'okusatu (Jjanwali 22, 2020).
Okukebera endwadde mu musaayi kwongerwako mu eddiyo ey'okuna (27 Jjanwali 2020) n'ey'okutaano (8 Febwali 2020); oluvannyuma, obujulizi obwa serology bwongerwako mu eddiyo ey'omusanvu.
Enkyukakyuka zino zeesigamye ku mulimu gw'abanoonyereza ku kunoonya ekikemo ekituufu eky'okwekebejja nucleic acid okusobola okuzuula ekirwadde mu bwangu, wamu n'ebifaananyi by'omu bbanga omuli okuggya omusaayi, nga waliwo ebika eby'enjawulo eby'ebitundu eby'enjawulo, era kyayambako mu kwongera okuzuula ekirwadde ky'ekikungo mu by'ebigenderwa ebikakasiddwa.
Ate era, waliwo obukakafu obugenda bweyongera obulaga nti tulina okwegendereza abalwadde abalina obubonero obutali bwa bulijjo n'abo abatalina bubonero.
N'olwekyo, ekifaananyi kya Zhou et al. kyetaaga okuddaabiriza kubanga baalaganga nti abantu abataalina bubonero bwa bulwadde balina akabi katono.
Enkola y'ebyenfuna nayo erina okwekebera mu nkola y'ekisawo ne mu by'okunoonyereza mu biseera eby'omu maaso.
Mu nkomerero, tusuubira obujulizi obwesigika era tusaba abasomi okuleetawo endowooza zaabwe.
Ku bikwata ku kumanya  abakakibwa nti balina obulwadde  n'abo abakakasibwa nti balina, tukubiriza abagenda okubufuna okugoberera n'okugoberera obulagirizi obusembayo obuliwo mu nsi yaabwe.
Ttiimu yaffe era ejja kutereeza ebiragiro byaffe mu kiseera ekituufu okusobola okuwa obuyambi.
Bangladesh erangiridde abantu bataano abaafudde COVID-19, omuwendo omupya ogusinga ogw'abantu abaafiira mu lunaku lumu
Eggulo, Bangladesh yakakasa abantu bataano abaafa COVID-19 mu lunaku lumu.
Mu kiseera kino, abantu abasoba mu 100 be bafiiridde mu ggwanga mu lunaku lumu olw'akawuka ka siriimu.
Eggulo, ekitongole kya Bangladesh Institute of Epidemiology, Disease Surveillance and Research (IEDCR) kyagambye nti omuwendo gw'abantu abazuuliddwa nga balina obulwadde buno gulimu abalwadde 114 ate 33 be bawonedde era nga bakyali mu maka gaabwe.
Abantu 17 be baafa.
Okuggalwa kw'ebidduka okutambula kwatandika nga March 26 era kwaliko ekigendererwa eky'okumalako ku Lwomukaaga, nga April 4.
Okusaabaza ebintu ebikulu (ebikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi, amafuta n'emmere) kyakkirizibwa.
Nga 19 March, abantu bano abasatu baali bawonye.
Ku Lwokuna, omuwendo gw'abantu bonna abalina ekirwadde kya Sars-CoV-2 mu nsi yonna gwali gusukka mu kakadde kamu, okusinziira ku lipoota okuva mu ttendekero lya Johns Hopkins.
Amawanga mangi mu nsi yonna gaalangirira nti galina okuteeka mu nkola ebintu ebirala ebikolebwako okuziyiza endwadde eno okusaasaana.
Ku Lwokuna, Loodi Meeya wa Moscow, Sergei Sobyanin, yayongera ku kiseera ky'okuziyiza abantu okuva mu kibuga okutuuka nga May 1.
Palamenti ya Portugal yasalawo okwongezaayo ennaku 15 mu budde obw'obudde obutali bwa bwenkanya; akalulu kaawedde n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwa 215 ku 10 n'obuvunaanyizibwa obwa 1.
Ensibuko y'obulwadde bwa coronavirus mu bantu
Obulwadde bwa SARS ne Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) bwayamba okulaga nti obulwadde bwa HCoV busobola okutabangula n'okutta abantu.
Mu ngeri y'emu, singa abantu bakwatibwa obulwadde bwa HCoVs, kiba kirungi okufuba okubuggya.
Mu ngeri y'emu, ekitundu ekimu eky'ekika kya HCoVs ekirimu ekitundu eky'omubiri ekiddiriŋŋana ky'ekika ekirala eky'ekika kya HCoVs.
