Ate era, obukuubagano obulala obukwata ku masiki bubaddewo mu mawanga amalala, gamba nga Germany, Austria ne Switzerland, awamu ne Czech Republic ne Italy.
Ate era, Turkey yawamba ebyuma ebikumi na bikumi ebikozesebwa mu kussa ebyuma eby'okukozesa mu kussa mu kasirise ebyalina okutwalibwa mu Spain.
Ku ntandikwa ya Maaki, gavumenti ya Italy yanenya nnyo olw'obutaba na bumu mu Yuniyooni y'e Bulaaya eri Italy, eyalina ekirwadde kya coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, omubaka wa Italy mu EU, yagambye nti China yokka ye yaddamu mu ngeri ey'obuvunaanyizibwa.
Kino tekitegeeza nti obumu mu Bulaaya buli mu mbeera nnungi.
Nga 22 omwezi gwa March, oluvannyuma lw'okumukubira essimu ne Katikkiro wa Italy Giuseppe Conte, Pulezidenti wa Russia Vladimir Putin yassaawo eby'enkola mu Russia okusindika abasawo mu magye, emmotoka ez'enjawulo ez'okusaanyaawo endwadde n'ebikozesebwa ebirala mu Italy.
Olupapula lw'amawulire oluyitibwa La Stampa olumu mu Italy lwakuba nga lukyogera ku muntu omu ow'obuyinza ow'ekitiibwa naye nga tamanyiddwa, yagamba nti ebitundu 80 ku buli kikumi eby'obuyambi obuva mu Russia tebyalina mugaso gwonna eri Italy.
Ensonda eno yalumiriza Russia nti etandise okulumba ensi mu ngeri ya geopolitics ne dipulomaasi.
Pulezidenti wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, ne Minisita w'ebyabufuzi mu Italy, Luigi Di Maio, bagaanye ebyogerwa mu mawulire era ne basiima.
Russia era yasindika ennyonyi etwala eby'obugagga eby'ekisawo mu Amerika.
Omwogezi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagamba nti, "Mu kuwaayo obuyambi eri bannaabwe mu Amerika, [Putin] atadde essira ku ky'okuba nti abakola ebyuma ebikozesebwa mu by'ekisawo mu Amerika bwe banaaba nga beeyongedde ku sipiidi, bajja kusobola okubayamba nabo bwe kinaaba kyetaagisa".
Okwegezaamu kw'amagye ga NATO okw'omwaka ogwokubiri mu Bugirimaani, Poland ne mu mawanga ga Baltic, okugezaamu okw'amagye agasingirayo ddala okuba okw'amaanyi okuva ku nkomerero ya Ssematalo ow'Okusiba, kujja kukendeezebwako.
Kati omuwaabi omukulu mu kaweefube w'okweggyako ebyokulwanyisa bya nukiriya Kate Hudson yanenya Defender 2020:  Mu mbeera ya kati ey'obulwadde bw'abantu, tekiteeka mu kabi obulamu bwa baserikale ba Amerika n'obw'amawanga ga Bulaaya mangi agali mu kaweefube, naye era n'obw'abantu mu nsi mwe baakola.  Gavumenti ya Iran yakosebwa nnyo obulwadde buno, nga bamemba ba palamenti 20 be bafuna obulwadde buno, awamu n'abalala 15 abaliko mu byobufuzi oba abaliko kati.
Pulezidenti wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yawandiika ebbaluwa eyanjulidde abakulembeze b'ensi yonna nga 14 Ogwokusatu, 2020, ng'agamba nti eggwanga lye lyali lifuba okulwanyisa ekirwadde kino olw'obutafuna buyinza ku butale bw'ensi yonna olw'ebibonerezo bya Amerika eri Iran. Ekirwadde kino kyaleetawo okukaaba okw'amaanyi eri Amerika okutwala enkola z'abantu ez'ensi yonna ez'amawanga amalala amagagga, omuli obujjanjabi obwa bonna, enteekateeka z'okulabirira abaana, okuwummula abazadde nga basasulwa, n'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu eby'obugagga eby'ensi yonna.
Abakugu mu by'obufuzi basuubira nti kino kijja kukosa nnyo ku ddembe lya Donald Trump ery'okuddamu okulondebwa mu kalulu k'obwapulezidenti aka 2020. Enkolagana wakati wa Japan ne South Korea zaali mbi nnyo olw'ekirwadde kino.
Korea ey'ebukiika ddyo yanenya  okufuba kwa Japan okw'okusiba abantu mu kaduukulu  oluvannyuma lw'e Japan okulangirira nti omuntu yenna ava mu Korea ey'ebukiika ddyo ajja kusibibwa mu kaduukulu okumala wiiki bbiri mu bifo ebyalondebwa gavumenti.
Abantu ba South Korea mu kusooka baali ba njawulo ku ngeri Pulezidenti Moon Jae-in gye yakwatamu ekizibu kino.
Abantu bangi mu Korea baateeka omukono ku kiwandiiko nga beegayirira Moon avunaanibwe olw'engeri embi gavumenti gye yakwatamu ekirwadde kino oba nga basiima engeri gye yakiddamu.
Abawandiisi abamu baalaze okutya nti kino kiyinza okuleetera gavumenti okwongera amaanyi.
Mu Hungary, palamenti yavuganya okuleka Katikkiro, Viktor Orbán, okufuga nga yeeyambisa amateeka okutuusa nga waliwo ekirala, okuyimiriza palamenti awamu n'okulonda, era n'okubonereza omuntu yenna avunaanibwa okugabana amawulire ag'obulimba ku kawuka ne gavumenti engeri gye yeeyisizzaamu ku kizibu kino.
Omulwadde gwa coronavirus guvunaaniddwa olw'ebitundu ebiwerako eby'okuyimirizibwawo kw'ebikozesebwa, okuva ku kweyongerayongera kw'omuwendo gw'ebikozesebwa okulwanyisa obulwadde, okwekulakulanya mu kugula ebintu, n'okuyimirizibwa kw'emirimu gy'amakolero n'ebikozesebwa.
Ekitongole ky'Amerika ekikola ku mmere n'eddagala kifulumizza okulabula ku bbula ly'eddagala n'eby'obujjanjabi olw'okweyongera kw'obwetaavu bw'abantu n'okuyimirizibwawo kw'abo abaliwawa.
Ebifo bingi nabyo byayolekaganye n'okugula ebintu ebiteekeddwa mu bwangu nga kino kivuddeko ebisale eby'omugaso okubula, gamba ng'emmere, empapula z'ekyokuna n'amazzi, ebirime, n'ebbula ly'ebintu.
Mu ngeri ey'enjawulo, ekitongole ky'eby'eby'enkulaakulana kye ky'avudde ku kulwawo okusindika ebintu eby'emikono.
Okusinziira ku akulira WHO, Tedros Adhanom, obwetaavu bw'eby'okwerinda obw'omubiri bweyongedde emirundi 100.
Kino kyaleetawo okweyongerayongera mu bbeeyi nga kusukka emirundi 20 ku gy'obadde osasula era kyaleetawo okusobya mu byuma by'ekisawo okumala emyezi ena oba mukaaga.
Kino era kivuddemu ebbula ly'ebikozesebwa okwetooloola ensi yonna era WHO erangiridde nti kino kijja kwonoona obulamu bw'abasawo.
Mu Australia, ekirwadde kino kiwadde abalimi omukisa okutunda ebintu bya Australia mu China.
Omulimu guno gwaleetawo ebbula ly'amabeere mu supamaketi era oluvannyuma gavumenti ya Australia n'agiwera. Wadde nga waliwo abantu bangi abalina COVID-19 mu bukiikakkono bwa Italy ne mu kitundu kya Wuhan, era nga kino kyaviirako abantu okwetaaga emmere ey'amaanyi, ebitundu bino ebibiri tebyalina bwetaavu bwa mmere.
Ebikolwa bya China ne Italy ku by'okutereka n'okutunda ebikozesebwa eby'omugaso mu ngeri emenya amateeka byavaamu ebirungi, ne kiziyiza ebbula ly'emmere eryali lyasuubirwa mu Bulaaya ne mu North America.
Olw'ebbeeyi y'ebirime, ebitundu by'obukiika obwa kkono byali tebikose nnyo, naye abasuubuzi bagamba nti ebbeeyi y'ebirime eyinza okwongera.
Emigga gy'emmere gyagulwawo okumala akaseera, ne mu kibuga Wuhan, nga gavumenti ya China eggulawo emizigo gy'ebisolo eby'embizzi okusobola okulabirira abantu.
Amateeka ng'ago gaateekebwawo mu Italy okukakasa nti abakola emmere balina ebintu bye basobola okukozesa mu mbeera ng'eyo ey'akabi.
Ebizibu mu by'enfuna by'ensi yonna byaliwo mu China: okusinziira ku alipoota y'amawulire eya Maaki 16, eby'enfuna mu China byayonooneka nnyo mu myezi ebiri egyasooka mu 2020 olw'ebyo gavumenti bye yakola okukendeeza okubuna kwa akawuka, era n'obutunda bw'ebitundutundu bwagwa ebitundu 20.5 ku buli kikumi.
Olw'okuba China y'ensi esinga obukulu mu by'enfuna ne mu by'okupangisa, kyazuulibwa nti ekirwadde kya kawuka kyali kiviirako ensi yonna okufiirwa enkulaakulana.
Agathe Demarais okuva mu kitongole kya Economist Intelligence Unit yagamba nti ebyenfuna bijja kusigala nga bikyukakyuka okutuusa nga tufunye ekifaananyi ekituufu eky'ebyo ebiyinza okuvaamu.
Mu Jjanwali 2020, abawandiisi abamu baalowooza nti ebyenfuna ebiva ku kawuka kano ku kukulaakulana kw'ensi yonna biyinza okusingako ebyo ebyava ku kawuka ka SARS aka 2002-2004.
Omuwandiisi w'ebyenjigiriza mu Washington University mu St. Louis yalagula nti enkola eno eyinza okubaako obuzibu bwa buwumbi 300 ku nsi yonna era nga eyinza okutwala emyaka ebiri.
Ekibiina ky'amawanga agatunda amafuta (OPEC) kigambibwa nti kifunye obutakkaanya oluvannyuma lw'omuwendo gwa mafuta okukka wansi olw'ebbeeyi y'amafuta okukendeera mu China.
Ebivvulu by'ensi yonna by'ebya bugagga byagwa ku February 24 olw'enkula y'omuwendo gw'abantu abalwadde COVID-19 ebweru wa China.
Ku Lwokuna 27, olw'okutya okw'amaanyi okwekiriko olw'ekirwadde kya ssenyiga omukambwe, ebitebe by'amaduuka mu Amerika omuli NASDAQ-100, S&amp;P 500 ne Dow Jones Industrial Average byafuna okukendeera okungi okuva mu 2008, Dow Jones n'egwa 1,191, era nga kwe kukendeera okunene mu lunaku lumu okuva mu buzibu bw'ebyensimbi obwaliwo mu 2007-08.
Ensonga zonna essatu zaawera wiiki nga zikendedde ebitundu 10 ku buli kikumi.
Nga Febwali 28, Scope Ratings GmbH yakakasa ebiteeso bya China, naye n'asigala ng'alina endowooza embi.
Emigabo gy'obugagga gyaddamu okukajja, olw'okutya ekirwadde kya coronavirus, era okukendeera okusingawo kwaliwo nga Maaki 16.
Bangi balowooza nti embeera y'eby'enfuna eyinza okuddawo.
Omusuubuzi Mohamed El-Erian yatendereza enteekateeka ez'obweggasi ezaateekebwawo mu budde obutuufu ne bbanka z'ensi n'amawanga.
Bbanka z'ensi ez'omunda zikwatagana mangu okusinga bwe zaakola mu kuzika kw'ebyenfuna mu 2008.
Eddwaliro lye limu ku magye agasinga okukosebwa olw'ebiragiro eby'okuziyiza okutambula, okuggyawo ebifo ebikwatagana n'abantu, naddala ebifo ebisikiriza abalambuzi, n'ebiragiro bya gavumenti ebigaana okutambula mu nsi yonna.
N'ekyavaamu, kampuni z'ennyonyi nnyingi zaggyako ennyonyi ezaali zeetaaga, gamba nga British Airways, China Eastern Airlines ne Qantas, ate nga Flybe, kampuni y'ennyonyi eya Bungereza eya Flybe, yafuna obuzibu.
Enkonge zino zaali zaali za maanyi nnyo mu kiseera ekyo.
Ebifo ebingi eby'eggaali y'omukka n'ebifo we batambulira ebyombo nabyo byaggalwa.
Obulwadde buno bwabaddewo ku Chunyun, ekiseera eky'obutembeeyi ekikulu ekikwataganyizibwa n'omwaka omuggya mu China.
Emikolo mingi egibaamu abantu abangi nnyo gyaggibwako enkola gavumenti z'ensi n'ez'ebitundu, omuli n'emikolo gy'omwaka omupya, era n'ebitongole by'obwannannyini nabyo byaggyawo amaduuka n'ebifo ebisikiriza abalambuzi, gamba nga Hong Kong Disneyland ne Shanghai Disneyland.
Embaga nnyingi ez'omwaka omupya zaaggyibwawo era ebifo bingi eby'obwananyirizi byaggalwawo okusobola okwewala okubeerayo abantu bangi, omwali ekibuga ekiyitibwa Beijing Forbidden City n'ebifo eby'obulambuzi eby'ekinnansi.
Mu bifo 24 ku 31 mu China, ab'obuyinza bongedde ekiseera ky'oluwummula olw'omwaka omupya okutuuka nga February 10, nga balagira abantu abasinga obungi obutaddamu kukola okutuusa nga February 10.
Ebitundu bino byali bibalirira ebitundu 80 ku 100 ku GDP y'eggwanga era ne 90 ku 100 ku 100 ku byamaguzi ebikolebwa ebweru.
Hong Kong yenyigira mu kulwanyisa endwadde ez'okusaanyaawo era n'alangirira embeera ey'obulabe, n'aggyawo amasomero okutuusa mu Maaki era n'eggyako emikolo gy'omwaka omupya. Embeera y'eby'amaguzi mu nsi yonna yakosebwa, n'ebiseera eby'amasamasa eby'amasimu eby'okuziguza eby'amaguzi ne biggibwawo oba n'amasiro ag'ebbeeyi ag'ekiseera.
Okukyala mu bakolero mu Bulaaya ne Latini Amerika kwakendeera ebitundu 40 ku buli kikumi.
Mu Amerika ey'ebukiikakkono ne mu Buvanjuba, abaguzi baalaba okukendeera kw'ebitundu 50 ku buli 100 oba 60 ku buli 100.
Kino era kyaviirako okutambula kw'abatambuza ebigere mu maduuka okutono ennyo mu Maaki ng'okugeraageranya ne Febwali, okugwa wakati wa 33 ne 43 ku buli 100 mu Maaki.
Abapangisa b'amaduuka okwetooloola ensi baalagira ebikolwa ebirala, gamba ng'okwongera ku bungi bw'abantu abayonja, okuteekawo ebikozesa ebipima ebbugumu ly'omubiri okuzuula obubugumu bw'abasitoma, n'okukomya emikolo. Okusinziira ku kiteeberezebwa ekitongole kya UN Economic Commission for Latin America, okukendeera kw'ensi okuleeteddwa ssenyiga omukambwe kuyinza okuviirako abantu abali wakati w'obukadde 14 ne 22 okubeera mu bwavu mu Latin America bw'obageraageranya n'embeera ey'obubenje.
Mu Jjanwali ne Febwali 2020, mu kiseera ekyasinze okuba ekizibu mu Wuhan, abantu obukadde nga 5 mu China baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe.
Mu China, bangi ku basenze abakola mu byalo abasoba mu bukadde 300 baasigala mu maka gaabwe mu bitundu by'omunda oba mu ssaza ly'e Hubei. Mu March 2020, abantu abasukka mu bukadde 10 mu Amerika baafiirwa emirimu gyabwe ne basaba gavumenti okubayamba.
Obukwakkulizo bwa Kolonaviirusi busobola okufiiriza emirimu egisoba mu bukadde 47 mu Amerika, ate obutali bwakola buyinza okutuuka ku 32%, okusinziira ku kubalirira kwa Federal Reserve Bank of St. Louis. Okusibawo kwa Yuganda kuleese obukadde n'obukadde bw'abakozi b'e Yuganda abava mu nsi endala nga tebalina mulimu. Okunoonyereza kwa Angus Reid Institute kwalaga nti ebitundu 44 ku buli kikumi mu maka g'e Canada bafunye obutali bw'emirimu obumu. Abalimu kumpi 900,000 mu Spain bafiiriddwa emirimu okuva ku kusibira kw'obubudamo mu makkati ga March 2020.
Mu kitundu eky'okubiri ekya Maaki, abakozi abafalansa obukadde 4 baasabye okufuna obuyambi bw'obutaba na mulimu ate abakozi aba Bungereza obukadde 1 ne basaba okwewola ssente z'omulembe.
Enkola y'omu Bugirimaani ey'okusasula abakozi abakola ekiseera ekitonotono yagobererwa mu Bufalansa ne Bungereza.
Ebikwata ku bifaananyi n'obusika bikoseddwa nnyo ekirwadde kino, ekireeseewo enkyukakyuka mu bitongole n'abantu kinnoomu, abeesalirawo n'abakozesa ku kigero eky'ensi yonna.
Ebibiina by'obuwangwa n'ebitone byafuba okukuuma obuvunaanyizibwa bwabyo (obutera okuweebwa ssente gavumenti) okuleeta eby'obugagga mu kitundu, okukuuma abakozi n'abantu, n'okuwagira abayimbi buli we kisoboka.
Mu Maaki 2020, okwetooloola ensi yonna mu mitendera egy'enjawulo, amadiba g'ebitabo, amaduuka ag'eby'emizannyo n'ebitongole ebirala eby'obuwangwa byaggalwa okutuusa nga bwe birategeezebwa era n'ebikolwa, emikolo n'emizannyo byago ne biggibwawo oba ne bisuulibwa.
Mu kwanukula, waabaddewo okufuba okw'amaanyi okugaba obuweereza obw'enjawulo okuyita mu byuma by'oku mutimbagano. Ekirala ekizze kibaawo mu kiseera kino era ekyeyongedde okusaasaana kwe kukendeezaako okulongoosa mu misomo gy'eddiini, emizannyo emikulu n'ebikolwa ebirala eby'abantu abangi, gamba ng'embaga z'ennyimba n'ebivvulu, enkuŋŋaana z'eby'ekipimo n'emikolo gy'eby'engoye.
Enkola y'okuzannya firimu nayo yalemwa, era Vatican yalangirira nti okukuza wiiki entukuvu mu Rome, ekikolebwa mu wiiki esembayo mu kiseera ky'okwejjusa mu Lw'okusiiba, kwaggibwawo.
Amadiikoni mangi gakubirizza bannamukadde okubeera awaka mu kifo ky'okugenda mu misa ku Ssande; amakanisa agamu gakasaasaanya enjiri zaabwe ku leediyo, ku mutimbagano ne mu butambi oba ku ttivi; ate amadiikoni amalala gakubiriza okusinziza mu mmotoka.
Okufaananako Diocese ya Rooma ey'Ekikatuliki eyaggirawo amakanisa gaayo n'amasaali era ne St. Peter's Square ey'omu kibuga ekikadde, amadiini amalala nago gakyusa enkuŋŋaana zaabwe era ne gakugira abantu okukuŋŋaana mu makanisa, emisirijja, amasinagogi, yeekaalu, ne mu ma gurdwaras.
Minisita w'ebyobulamu mu Iran yalangirira okuyimiriza okusaba kw'Olwokutaano mu bitundu ebikwatiddwa ekirwadde kino era ebifo ebitukuvu ne biggalwa, ate Saudi Arabia yawera abagwira n'abantu baayo okuyingira ebifo ebitukuvu mu Mecca ne Medina.
Obulwadde buno buleesewo okutaataaganyizibwa okw'amaanyi mu misomo gy'ensi yonna okuva ku Ssematalo II.
Emizannyo emikulu ennyo gy'egyalemeddwako oba okuyimirizibwawo, omuli UEFA Champions League 2019-20, UEFA European Championship 2019-20, UEFA Euro 2020, NBA 2019-20, ne NHL 2019-20.
Obulwadde buno bwataatabula emizannyo gya Olympics eya 2020 eya Summer, nga yatandika ku nkomerero ya Jjulaayi; International Olympic Committee yalangirira nga 24 Maaki nti omukolo gwandisuubirwa okusukka 2020, naye nga gwakusingidde mu by'obutiti bya 2021. Kazino n'ebifo ebirala eby'emizannyo okwetooloola ensi yonna byaggalwawo, era empaka za poker eziriwo zaali zisengekeddwa oba zaabadde zaagobwa.
Kino kyaleetera abazannyi bangi okwewandiisa ku mutimbagano, era ebifo bingi eby'okuzannyisa ku mutimbagano byalabye okwongera kw'abantu abazze bewandiisa. Emizannyo gy'eby'amasanyu nabyo byayonoonebwa, nga ebibiina by'abayimbi bingi biremesezza oba biggyawo ebivvulu byabwe.
Amaduuka mangi agaali gagenda okuzannya emizannyo, gamba nga ku Broadway, nago gaasannyalala.
Abawandiisi abamu banoonyezza engeri z'okweyongera okutonda n'okugabana emirimu gyabwe ku mutimbagano nga mu kifo ky'enkola y'okukuba emizannyo ku mutimbagano, gamba nga okuyimba ku mutimbagano oba emikolo gy'oku mutimbagano egitegekeddwa abayimbi okuzannya, okusaasaanya n'okutumbula emirimu gyabwe.
Ku mutimbagano, emyoyo mingi ku yintaneti ku nsonga ya coronavirus gyasaasaanye kubanga bangi baagala nnyo okusekerera n'okusanyusa mu maaso g'obutabeera na bumanyirivu.
Okuva COVID-19 lwe yatandika, okusosola, obukyayi eri abantu abalala n'obusosoze byeyongedde eri abantu ab'omu China ne East Asia, n'abantu abava mu bitundu by'e Bulaaya, Amerika n'ensi endala.
Embeera ez'okutya, okwekengera n'obukyayi zaalabikira mu nsi nnyingi, naddala mu Bulaaya, Asiya ow'ebuvanjuba, North America ne mu kitundu kya Asia Pacific.
Lipoota okuva mu February (ng'ebisinga obungi ku bantu abaakosebwa obulwadde buno bakyali mu China) zaalaga endowooza z'obwenkanankana mu bibiina ebitali bimu okwetooloola ensi nti abantu b'omu China baali bagwana okubalumirirwa oba okubonerezebwa.
Ensi ezimu mu Afirika nazo zalabye okwongera kw'obukyayi eri Abachina.
Abantu bangi mu Wuhan ne Hubei baategeezezza nti basosolwa olw'ekifo we baava.
Obuyambi buweereddwa eri abantu b'omu China, ka babe nga bali ku mutimbagano oba ku nsi yonna, n'abantu abali mu bitundu ebiriddwako akawuka.
Olw'okuba ekirwadde kino kigenda kyeyongera okusaasaana mu nsi endala ezirina obuzibu, abantu b'omu Italy, ensi esoose mu Bulaaya okufuna ekirwadde kya COVID-19, nabo bayinza okuteeberezebwa n'okuziyizibwa. Abantu b'omu nsi nga Malaysia, New Zealand, Singapore ne South Korea baasooka okuteeka emikono ku kiwandiiko ekiraga nti bagala okugaana abantu b'omu China okuyingira mu nsi yaabwe basobole okuziyiza ekirwadde kino.
Mu Japan, hashtag #ChineseDontComeToJapan yafuna omuliro ku Twitter.
Ab'omu China n'Aba-Asiya abalala ababeera mu Bungereza ne Amerika baategeezezza nti waliwo ebikolwa bingi eby'obusosoze n'okulumya abantu.
