Mu mwezi guno, tuli mu mbeera ey'enjawulo.
Obulwadde bwa COVID-19 bukakasa bulungi enkolagana yaffe ey'ensi yonna n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwe tulina eri bannaffe.
Obuzibu bwe butabangawo, naye tumanyi nti engeri esingayo obulungi gye tuyinza okwanukulamu kwe kuba nti tulina empisa, obumu n'okunyweza oluganda mu nsi yonna, nga bino bye biri mu mutima gw'ekibiina kino.
Enkolagana ennungi gye tulabye mu b'oluganda bonna mu mmesegi, essimu, ne mu mboozi ez'omu butanwa bukakafu bwa maanyi obulaga nti tuli bantu balungi nnyo.
Sisobola kwongera kusiima na kwetulinkiriza okusinga mmwe mwenna abali ku ludda lwange.
Wiiki ewedde, waliwo omuntu eyaŋŋamba nti asiima omulimu gwaffe.
Omuntu ono yanzijjukiza obukulu bw'ensi okuyinza okwekenneenya Wikipedia mu kiseera kino, era n'obukulu bw'ekifaananyi ky'obukulu bw'ekintu kino eky'omugaso okusigala nga kiri ku mutimbagano era nga kisobola okufunibwa buli omu.
Kino kisobose olw'omulimu gwammwe, ka kibe nga mukuuma ebifo byaffe nga bikolera, nga mutuusa bakozi baffe ku mpeke oba nga mukuuma ebifo byaffe nga birimu obukuumi.
Ensi yeetaaga obubaka obuva mu Wikipedia, kati okusinga bwe kyali.
Kino kye kiseera, si ebyo byokka bye tukola, naye n'engeri gye tubikolamu, by'ebinaakola ku nsi.
Olw'obukulu bw'omulimu guno n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwammwe, tugenda kukola enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi mu ngeri gye tukolera wamu okuva wiiki ejja.
Okukola Enkyukakyuka mu Nkola Yaffe n'Embeera
Nga Robyn bwe yayogeddeko waggulu, ttiimu yakwana ekiro ekyasembayo okwogerako ku ngeri gye tugenda okutambulamu n'enteekateeka zaffe mu nnaku n'emyezi egenda okujja.
Mu mboozi eyo, twalowooza ku ngeri gye tuyinza okuddamu embeera gye twolekaganye nayo era n'engeri gye tuyinza okukuuma ekibiina nga kibeerawo mu kiseera kino.
Ekisooka, twali twagala okweggyamu okweraliikirira era n'okuwagira omulimu gwaffe ogw'ekiseera kyonna.
Bw'oba ng'olina w'oyinza okuggya ebirowoozo byo, toyanguyiriza.
Bonna abakozi, abapangisa n'abapangisa endagaano:
Ekigendererwa kyaffe eky'ebiseera by'okukola buli lunaku kiribeera essaawa nga 4 buli lunaku, oba essaawa 20 buli wiiki okutuusa nga waliwo ekirala.
Tetukola lunaku lwa luwummula: bw'oba ng'osobola okukola essaawa ez'emirundi egisingawo, oyinza okuba ow'omugaso eri omulimu.
Kyokka, ensi ya leero tetegeerekeka, era bw'oba olina okulabirira abaagalwa bo, okugula ebintu, oba okugenda okulaba omusawo, obulungi bwo kye kintu kye tukulembeza.
Tetukebera biseera by'omala nga weenyigira mu mulimu gw'okubuulira.
Bw'oba olwadde, tolina kukola.
Tekyetaagisa kwogera, naye tubyogera.
Tewali kuwummula kw'olwala oba ku luwummula olusasulwa: buulira mukama wo era oyambe ttiimu yo okukyusa mu kalenda n'enteekateeka z'emirimu okukakasa nti ebitundu ebikulu eby'emirimu bikwatiddwa.
(Bw'oba okeberebwa ne bakukebera COVID-19, tuukirira Bryan okuva mu kitongole kya T&C Ops akuyambe era akakase nti embeera yo efuna okulabirirwa okwetaagisa okuva mu baaminsita).
Abakozi abali ku ssaawa bajja kusasulwa mu bujjuvu.
Kino tukitegedde era tukiggumiza nti tulina okutuukiriza obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe eri bakolopoota baffe n'abakozi abalala.
Buli muntu ajja kusasulwa okusinziira ku ssaawa ze yakolanga mu mbeera eza bulijjo.
Kino kikola ne bw'oba nga tolina busobozi kukola.
Bw'oba oyagala okukola, tukugoberera.
Abantu bangi bakozesa emirimu ng'engeri y'okwekangamu okweraliikirira okw'ensi eno.
Kye tukola kiyinza okuba eky'omuganyulo ennyo, naddala mu biseera nga bino.
Ne ku luno, ekigendererwa kwe kukuuma.
Tukusaba gusabe ne mukama wo, tumanyire bye tusuubira era tusobole okukola enteekateeka.
Emirimu egimu gitwalibwa okuba egikulu.
Waliwo ebintu bye tulina okweyongera okukola.
Ttiimu za SRE, Ops HR, Trust &amp; Safety, ne Fundraising (n'endala) zirina omulimu omukulu gwe zikola era bayinza okwetaaga obuyambi.
Tugenda kutandikawo enkola n'ebitongole byonna okuteebereza ebiruubirirwa byaffe era twemalire ku kuwagira emirimu egikulu mu mulimu gwaffe.
Waliwo emirimu emingi gye tulina okukola, tugenda kumalira ebirowoozo byaffe ku mirimu emikulu egisinga.
Bw'onootereeza mu kiseera kino, tojja kuddamu kuddirira.
Tetulina kigendererwa kya kukola mirundi ebiri okusobola okuzzaawo obudde bwe tumaze nga twolekedde obulwadde buno.
Tetujja kukugamba kukola ku ssaawa ezisukka mu ezo ez'omulundi ogumu okusobola okutuukiriza ekintu ky'otoyinza kutuukiriza.
Tukimanyi nti embeera zikyuse, era tujja kufuba okuteekawo ebiruubirirwa ebipya n'ebiseera ebipya nga bwe kisoboka.
Ate PPP (Planning Annual) ey'omwaka?
Okusobola okutuukana n'embeera yaffe empya n'ebiruubirirwa byaffe eby'ebiseera by'okukola, tusuubira okukyusa essaawa ey'okuwaayo Enteekateeka yaffe ey'omwaka 2020-2021.
Tusuubira okugaziya ku nteekateeka yaffe eya 2019-2020 eyongere okuteekawo ebiseera ebisaana mu kutegeka embalirira, kisobozese abakozi okuteeka ebirowoozo ku mirimu gyabwe egy'omugaso, okwerabirira awamu n'abaagalwa baabwe, nga bakolera wamu n'abo abeetaaga oba abaagala okukendeeza ku ssaawa ze bakola mu wiiki ezijja.
Okweyongera kuno ku biseera eby'omuggalo, kukendeeza nnyo ku mulimu n'okunyigirizibwa kw'okuteekateeka okw'omu kiseera kino mu kibiina kyonna.
Tugenda kuteeka ekiteeso kyaffe mu Kakiiko w'ebyokulonda wiiki ejja era tugenda kutegeeza abakiise n'ebitongole ebiddako nga tukakasibwa.
Tumwebaza ku bukulembeze bw'ekitongole kya APP mu nsonga eno.
Ekifo, okuteekawo n'okuyonja ofiisi
Wiiki ewedde, twafuna amawulire nti omu ku bakozi bannaffe mu San Francisco ayinza okuba nga yalumbibwa akawuka ka COVID-19.
Kyokka, olw'obwegendereza, twateekawo ekibinja ky'abasawo abafuba okulwanyisa obuwuka obuleeta obulwadde mu ofiisi yaffe ey'omu San Francisco.
Baakozesa eddagala erivumita endwadde ez'omu ddwaliro okufuuyira buli kifo, awamu n'ekisenge ky'okuyingira n'ebifo ebiwerako ebiva ku lifti okutuuka ku mwaliiro gwaffe.
Ekizimbe kino kikola ku nkola yaakyo ey'okulabirira ekizimbe era nga kikozesa ebintu ebikuuma abatuuze baayo.
Tuli bakakafu nti ofiisi eno ejja kuba ng'etegekeddwa bulungi nga tuzzeeyo.
Ofiisi yaffe mu Washington DC esangibwa mu weema ya WeWork, eyagabana naffe n'abakozi bonna ab'omu Washington DC enteekateeka yaayo ey'okwewala COVID-19.
Okuva wiiki ewedde, ofiisi yaffe mu Washington DC yatandikawo enkola ey'okubeera ku ntambula ey'ekyaama nga bwe baalagirwa mu San Francisco.
Nga abamu ku abo be tukola nabo mu New York bwe bakimanyi, twasalawo okupangisa ekizimbe mu Brooklyn.
Okwogera kuno kugenda mu maaso naye kuyinza okuyimirirwa.
Abamu ku bakozi bannaffe, guno gwe mulundi gwe ogusoose okukola nga bali wala okuva we babeera.
Banno abaamanyiira okukola emirimu nga bali wala bakimanyi nti kiyinza obutaba kyangu okutambulako era baagala kukuwa amagezi:
Kendeezaamu ku budde bw'enkuŋŋaana oziggyeko essaawa emu oba bbiri.
Bwe kiba kyetaagisa, muyinza okufunangayo ekiseera ne mukola ebintu ebirala.
Kirage nti olukuŋŋaana lukulu, olina enteekateeka ya lunaku, era nti ebitabo by'olukuŋŋaana bijja kusindikibwa nga bukyali.
Okufuula vidiyo ekintu ekisangibwa ennyo, nga tukozesa eby'okukozesa nga Google Docs ne Zoom okukubiriza okukolagana n'okuwuliziganya mu butereevu.
Beera n'omuwabuzi w'enkuŋŋaana, omuntu akuuma emboozi n'olubu lw'aboogera, n'omuntu akuyamba mu kuwandiika (oba okuwandiika mu ngeri ey'ekikubiro).
Oyinza okuwandiikira abasambi obubaka ku ssimu bw'oba nga weetaaga ekikutu ky'okuwulira obulungi.
Kozesa ssente z'ofuna ku ssente z'obutonde bwo okufunamu emmere.
Ku Slack, genda ku #remoties channel oyogere ne bakozi banno abakola mu kitongole ekitegeka emirimu.
Ekibinja ky'emirimu gya HR ky'ekola ku mitendera gy'emirimu egigenda mu maaso nga kyesigamiziddwa ku webinars okuwagira okwongera okugabana emirimu mu kitongole.
Wiiki ewedde, twasabye abaweebwa ensimbi z'ekibiina bonna bakendeeze ku mikolo gy'abantu bonna egigendereddwamu Wikimedia, gamba nga edit-a-thons, okutuusa nga WHO etegeezezza nti ekirwadde kiwedde.
Twabategeeza nti tukimanyi nti okusaba kwaffe okw'okuggyawo ebbago eryo n'ebirala ebirimu biyinza okulemesa enteekateeka zaabwe ez'okugaba ssente era nti tewali muntu yenna agenda kubonerezebwa singa ebiruubirirwa byabwe biwambibwa oba bikyusibwa.
Mu wiiki ejja, tujja kufulumya ebiragiro ebirala ku Wikimania n'enkuŋŋaana endala ez'ekitundu n'ez'ekitundu.
Enneewulira mu nsi yonna erabika ng'eri emu ey'ennaku olw'enkyukakyuka eno era n'okubudaabudibwa olw'okutegeera obulungi era n'okusobola okussa ebirowoozo byabwe ku bantu baabwe, Wikimedia n'ebirala.
Ku nsonga ey'okugenda mu maaso, CRT ekola ku kutondawo olupapula ku Meta-Wiki okuwa ekifo abantu mwe bayinza okulabira enkulaakulana n'okwongera okuwuliziganya nabo.
Okweyongera okuwuliziganya wadde nga waliwo ebizibu ebiva ku COVID-19
Tujja kutumira abantu mu kalenda zammwe okujja mu lukiiko olutabalika lwa bakozi ku Lwokuna lw'omwaka ogujja, ku ssaawa 2:00 ez'ekiro mu kiseera kyaffe (UTC) ku ssaawa 7:00 ez'olweggulo mu kiseera kyaffe (PT).
Tukozesa ekiseera kino okuwuliziganya ku bintu ebirala, okuddamu ebibuuzo byammwe, n'okubeerako awamu.
Kino kitukwatako ffenna era tuli wano okukuyamba mu ngeri yonna.
Okutuusa olwo, osobola okusanga obubaka obuli mu bubaka buno, n'ebirala byonna ebikulu ebikwata ku COVID-19, ku Office Wiki.
CRT ejja kutereeza empapula ezo era n'ekuŋŋaanya obubaka bwonna mu kifo kimu.
Era tufuba okuba n'empuliziganya ennungi n'abakozi abali mu nsi ezirimu obulwadde buno.
Bw'oba olina ebibuuzo ebikwata ku ntambula, emikolo, emirimu emikulu, oba obuzibu bw'okufuna amawulire, oba ekintu kyonna ky'oyagala okufuna obuyambi, tolonzalonza kututegeeza era okole ne CRT.
Tuli wano okukuwa obuyambi n'okufuna akakwate we kyetaagibwa.
Bweba balina ebibuuzo eby'obwannannyini oba eby'obumativu, beewandiise eri Bryan Judan, akulira eby'okulonda mu nsi yonna mu HR.
Tewali na kimu ku nkyukakyuka zino kyewandirowoozezza nti ky'okulekawo omulimu gwaffe n'obuvunaanyizibwa bwaffe.
Wabula, kyetaagisa okumanya nti emirimu gyaffe n'obuvunaanyizibwa biyinza okwetaaga okukyusibwa mu ngeri etannatuuka.
Emitendera gino gye tutwala nga gyetaagisizza okusobola okuwagiragana n'okweyongera mu mulimu gwaffe, okuleeta obuyambi bwonna obubeetaagisa, n'okuweereza ensi nga buli omu bw'asobola okwesiga.
Omulimu gwaffe gwe twakola gwandibaddewo ng'ekiseera kituuse.
Kati kye kiseera okwetegekera n'okuyambagana emirimu emikulu egiri mu wiiki era oboolyawo emyezi egijja.
Twetaaga buli omu ku mmwe okutuukiriza ekyo, era kyekivudde kitwetaagisa okwerinda n'okulabirira ab'omu maka go, osobole okukola obulungi mu kiseera kino.
Okumaliriza, nkusaba: munaabe engalo era temukwata ku maaso!
Katherine, CRT (Amanda K, Amy V, Bryan J, Doreen D, Gregory V, Jaime V, Joel L, Lynette L, Ryan M, ne Tony S), n'abalala bonna ku ttiimu y'obuvunaanyizibwa (Grant I, Heather W, Jaime V, Janeen U, Lisa S, Robyn A, Ryan M, ne Toby N).
Ensiza eya ACE2 (Angiotensin converting enzyme 2) enziimu eri mu nda ez'ebweru (ku mmembaani z'ebirimu) ez'omu bwongo, emitima, enso, n'ebinywa.
LACE2 eremesa enzyme eyefuula angiotensin (ACE) okukola nga ekendeeza ku bungi bwa angiotensin II era n'okwongeza Ang (1-7) nga kino kifuula eddagala erisuubizo mu kujjanjaba endwadde z'omutima. LACE2 era y'ensibuko y'amasimu ag'akawuka ka corona.
Ensawo ya enziimu eno mu bantu etera okuyitibwa hACE2.
Enzyme eyitibwa angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) enzyme erina zinc mu z'obutundutundu obuli ku masiro g'ebisenge by'ensiri eby'omu mubiri (endothelial cells) n'ebirala.
Protein ACE2 erimu ekitundu kya peptidase ekirina enkomerero ya N, M2, n'ekitundu kya collectrin ekirina enkomerero ya C.
LACE2 y'omu ku puloteni ey'ekika ekimu ey'omubiri eyitibwa type I, nga enziimu yaayo erina ekitundu ekikolera ku masimu g'omu mawuggwe n'ebitundu ebirala.
Ekitundu kya ACE2 ekiva mu butoffaali bw'omubiri kikyusibwa okuva mu kitundu ekirala ekiyitibwa sheddase; ate amasavu agavaamu ne gayingizibwa mu musaayi ne gasumululwa mu kiwewa.
LACE2 esangibwa mu bitundu by'omubiri ebisinga: lACE2 esangibwa ku bbugwe w'obutundutundu bwa pulmonary alveolar type II, enterocytes mu byenda ebitono, endothelial cells mu mibiri n'ebisenge, ne mu mibiri egya musujja mu bitundu by'omubiri ebisinga.
ACE2 lmRNA era yeeyolekera mu bwongo, mu bwongo, mu bwongo, mu bwongo ne mu bwongo.
Omulimu gwa ACE2 gw'asooka kwe kuggya ACE.
LY'ACE eryawula angiotensin I okuva mu angiotensin II, ekirwanyisa obwagazi bw'omusaayi.
LACE2 nayo eyawula carboxyl amino acid eya phenylamine okuva mu angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) n'eyisamba mu angiotensin ey'okugaziya obusimu (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
LACE2 era esobola okusalaamu peptide endala ez'enjawulo omuli [des-Arg9]-bradykinine, lapelin, neurotensin, dynorphine A, ne ghrelin.
LACE2 era erongoosa okusaasaanya kwa SLC6A19 era nga y'emu ku bintu ebireeta obulwadde bwa Hartnup.
Ng'ekirungo ekikwatagana n'omubiri, ACE2 kye kisinga okuyingira mu buwuka bwa koronavirisi, omuli HCoV-NL63, SARS-CoV (akawuka akaleeta SARS), ne SARS-CoV-2 (akawuka akaleeta COVID-19).
Okusingira ddala, ekirungo kya S1 protein okuva mu SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV2 ku kitundu kya enzyme ekya ACE2 ku lusenge lw'ensiri kivaamu endocytosis ne translocation ya kawuka ne enzyme mu endosomes eziri munda mu lusenge.
Enkola eno ey'okuyingira era yeetaagisa protein S okukolebwa serine protease eya TMPRSS2, era okuziyiza kwa serine protease kati kunoonyerezaako ng'obujjanjabi obusookerwako. Kino kireetedde abamu okulowooza nti okukendeeza ku mutindo gwa ACE2 mu buto kiyinza okuyamba okulwanyisa obulwadde.
Kyokka, ebibiina by'abasawo n'ebitongole ebikuuma ddembe byalaga nti eddagala erya ACE inhibitor ne ARB lyandyeyongedde okukozesebwa.
Okunoonyereza okwakolebwa mu 2012 kwalaga nti  okukozesa ACE inhibitors kwakkaanya nnyo ebyago bya pneumonia ku 34% nga bakugeraageranya n'abo abaakozesebwa mu bujjanjabi. 
Okugatta ku ekyo, akabi k'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe kaali katono nnyo mu balwadde abajjanjabirwa ACE inhibitor abaali mu kabi k'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, naddala abo abaalina obulwadde bw'omutima n'obutafuna bujjanjabi.
Okukozesa ACE inhibitors nakyo kyalina akakwate n'okukendeeza okufa olw'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe, wadde nga ebyavudde mu kunoonyereza okwo byali bya maanyi okusinga ku ebyo eby'obulwadde bw'amawuggwe.
Enziimu eya human recombinant angiotensin 2 conversion enzyme (rhACE2) esuubizibwa okuba eddagala eddene mu kujjanjaba endwadde z'omu mawuggwe ez'amaanyi era kirabika ng'erongoosa obwagazi bw'omu mawuggwe n'omukka oguyitibwa oxygen saturation mu mbuzi eziriko obulwadde bwa lipopolysaccharide-induced acute respiratory distress syndrome.
Ekiseera ky'obuwanguzi bw'eddagala lino mu bantu kiri mu ddakiika 10 era nga kyongedde ku budde bw'obuwanguzi bw'eddagala lino okumala eddakiika 30 ng'oggyeeko obudde bw'obuwanguzi (obumalirivu) obuba buwanvu bwa ssaawa 24.
Ennyingi ez'ebyazuuliddwa biraga nti rhACE2 eyinza okuba eddagala ery'omukisa eri abantu abatalina buwombeefu ku bulwadde obuyitibwa classic renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS) oba endwadde ezirimu obuwuka obutereevu obw'omukka obuyitibwa angiotensin II. rhACE2 mu nnyindo yafuuliriziddwa mu kugezesebwa kw'eddagala mu kujjanjaba obulwadde bw'okusannyalazibwa okw'amaanyi mu nnyindo.
COVID-19 apps zikozesebwa ku ssimu ezikozesebwa mu kulondoola abantu be bakwataganye nabo mu kawumpuli wa ssenyiga omukambwe 2019-20, kwe kugamba, okumanya abantu (abo be twakwataganye nabo) abayinza okuba nga baliko omuntu gwe bakwataganye naye.
Waliwo enkola ez'enjawulo ezakolebwa oba ezaaweebwa, nga zikoleddwa gavumenti mu bitundu ebimu ne mu bitundu ebirala.
Enkola z'eby'obugagga ez'enjawulo zaakolebwa okusobozesa okukola programu z'okukebera abantu.
Enkola zino, naddala ezo ezisinziira ku kukebera ebifo abakozesa app we babeera, zireetawo ebibuuzo ebikwata ku bubeerawo bw'abantu.
Waliwo engeri endala ezitali za bulabe, omuli okukozesa obubonero bwa Bluetooth okuwandiika omukozesa bw'aba n'essimu endala.
Nga 10 Apuli 2020, Google ne Apple baalangirira wamu nti bagenda kussa mu nkola za Android ne iOS enkola eyinza okuyambako mu kutegeka programu zino eza Bluetooth.
Gavumenti ya China ng'ekolagana ne Alipay, yatandikawo app mu China esobozesa abantu okumanya oba nga baaliko abantu abalina COVID-19.
Eddwaaliro lino lirina ebitundu ebiwerako eby'omu China, era lirina n'ebibuga ebisoba mu 200.
Ekitongole kya NRM kyakuza programu ya Bluetooth eyitibwa StopKorona! , ekakasa nti abantu abalina obulwadde buno bakeberebwa mu ngeri y'okufuna obubaka obumala era n'okwanguya okuwuliziganya n'abakulu b'ebitongole ebikuuma obulamu bw'abantu.
App eno yateekebwawo Minisitule y'ebyempuliziganya n'ebyempuliziganya n'Ekitongole ky'ebyobulamu.
Nga 14 Apuli 2020, enkola ya app yali yeetaaga okukakasibwa mu Google Play Store ne Apple App Store.
Ku nga 12 Apuli, Gavumenti yagamba nti app ya kukebera abo be bakwataganye nayo yali mu mitendera egya waggulu era yali eyinza okukozesebwa mu wiiki ezijja.
Australia ne New Zealand ziteekateeka okussaawo app eza TraceTogether mu Singapore nga zisinziira ku nkola ya BlueTrace. Russia eteekateeka okussaawo app ey'okunoonyereza ku mbeera y'obudde eri abalwadde ba COVID-19 ababeera e Moscow okukakasa nti tebabava waka.
Ross Anderson, profesa wa Security Engineering mu Cambridge University, yayogedde ku bizibu eby'omunda ebiyinza okuva mu kukozesa enkola ezisinziira ku nkola, omuli enkola ey'obutabeera n'obwesimbu era n'obutaba na mugaso singa abantu batono nnyo ku bantu bonna be bakozesa enkola eyo.
Mu kwanukula okweraliikirira okwekwata ku kusaasaanyizibwa kw'enkola za  coronavirus  ez'obulimba oba ez'akabi, Apple ekkiriza ebibiina  eby'obwannannyini  oba ebitanyigirwamu okutwalira awamu okwongera ku nkola za coronavirus mu App Store.
Google ne Amazon nabo baateekawo amateeka ge gamu.
Abakuumi b'eby'obuntu baalaga okweraliikirira ku ngeri programu za coronavirus gye ziyinza okukozesebwa mu kulondoola abantu mu bungi, naddala ku ngeri enkola y'okulondoola abantu gye yandikozeseddwamu okuziyiza ekirwadde kya coronavirus ng'ekizze wala.
Amnesty International n'ebitongole ebirala ebisoba mu 100 bifulumizza ekiwandiiko nga bikubiriza okukendeeza ku kukuuma abantu mu ngeri eno.
Entegeka zino zaaliwo ebintu munaana ebirina okutuukirizibwa mu pulojekiti za gavumenti:
obulabirizi bw'ebikolobero bwandikkirizibwa mu mateeka, bwetaagisa era nga bweyenkanankana;
Okweyongera mu buyinza n'okukuumibwa kwandibadde kukwata ku by'okuggyawo;
Okukozesa kw'ebyo by'ofunye kulina kukakasibwa ku bigendererwa by'okulwanyisa COVID-19;
Obukuumi bw'obubaka n'obutabeerawo mu bujjuvu birina okukuumibwa mu ngeri esobola okweyoleka;
Okukeberera mu ngeri ey'ekibinja kyandikuumiddwa okwewala okwongera okusaasaanya n'okusala ekitundu;
Okugabana kwonna kw'obubaka n'abantu abalala kulina okuteekebwa mu tteeka;
Obukuumi okuva mu bukyamu n'okutuukirira abantu mu mbeera ey'obubbi bw'ebikolwa eby'obubbi bisaanidde okuteekebwawo;
 okwenyigira okw'amaanyi  ku b'omugaso bonna, naddala abakugu mu by'obulamu n'ebibinja ebyewaggula.
Enteekateeka ya Google/Apple ey'okugonjoola ekizibu ky'okweyongera okunoonyereza, egenda kuggyawo enkola y'okuzuula ebikolwa by'ebikozesebwa ku byuma byabwe nga tebikyetaagisa.
Amawanga agamu galiko enkola ya geolocation mu kifo kya app, ekibalemesa okussa mu nkola enkola ya app n'okwewala okulabibwa.
Mu Isiraeri, enkola y'okuteekawo embalirira y'amasannyalaze yakkirizibwa.
Enkola z'omukutu ezikozesa ebiwandiiko ebikalu bya geolocation biyinza okubaako obuzibu bwabyo.
