Ng'oggyeko okukozesa obubaka buno okulabula abantu be bayinza okukolagana nabo, gavumenti era yafuula obubaka bw'obw'okubeerawo eri abantu bonna, ekikkirizibwa oluvannyuma lw'enkyukakyuka ez'amaanyi ezaakolebwa mu mateeka agakuuma ebyama oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kwa MERS mu ggwanga.
Mu ngeri y'emu, mu nsi ezimu, abantu bangi basobola okuwulira obubaka obuli mu biwandiiko bya gavumenti, nga bakozesa ebiwandiiko ebiggya ebya gavumenti, nga bakozesa ebiwandiiko ebiggya ebya gavumenti, oba nga bakozesa ebiwandiiko ebiggya ebya gavumenti.
