Enkola zino z'okubeera nti obubaka obwekusiiga ku muntu tebuva ku kyuma era nti ebiwandikibwa byonna bikolebwa ku kyuma.
Ekibiina kya Privacy Group ekya MIT Media Lab kati kyesimbawo SafePaths, ekifo ekikozesebwa mu kukuuma ebyama nga bakuŋŋaanya era nga bakozesa ebifo oba emikwano okusobola okunoonya ekirwadde kya COVID-19.
Enkola eno yeesigamiziddwa ku biva mu kitabo ekiriko omuko ogugamba nti Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic ekyafulumizibwa mu March 2020.
SafeTrace ekozesa tekinologiya wa hardware omukuumi okuyamba abantu okugabana obubaka obukwata ku kifo n'ebyobulamu n'abalala n'abakulu b'ebitongole ebikuuma ddembe awatali kutta bantu.
Nga 5 Okitobba 2020, TCN International Coalition yateekebwawo ebibinja ebikuŋŋaanye nga byesigama ku nkola emu n'empisa ez'enjawulo ez'ekika ekyenkanankana, okukendeeza obunkenke n'okumaliriza okussa mu nkola okunoonyereza n'okulabula okw'ensi yonna, ekintu ekikulu mu kukkiriza abantu bangi.
