Abalala abawagira CEPI mu kukola eddagala ly'okwekakaanya COVID-19 be Moderna, Curevac, Inovio, Novavax, Yunivasite ya Hong Kong, Yunivasite ya Oxford ne Yunivasite ya Queensland.
