Mu 2020, tewali ddagala lya bulwadde bwa SARS eryazuulibwa nga liwonyezebwa oba nga liyamba abantu.
Okusinziira ku biwandiiko by'ebunoonyereza ebyafulumizibwa mu 2005 ne 2006, okunoonyereza n'okuteekawo eddagala ly'okuggya eddagala n'eddagala eriggya okujjanjaba SARS kyakulembezebwa nnyo gavumenti n'ebitongole by'ebyobulamu okwetooloola ensi yonna. Tewali ddagala erigezesebwa erwanyisa MERS.
MERS bwe yatandika okusaasaana, kyali kirowoozebwa nti okunoonyereza okwaliwo ku SARS kwandibadde nga kyakulabirako eky'okuteekateeka eddagala n'eddagala erirwanyisa obulwadde bwa MERS-CoV.
Mu Maaki 2020, eddagala limu erirwanyisa MERS (eryesigamiziddwa ku DNA) lyamalirizibwa mu bantu era n'endala ssatu zaali zikyali mu nkola; eddagala lyonna lyali lya bulwadde, bbiri zaali za bulwadde bwa mukenenya (ChAdOx1-MERS, BVRS-GamVac) ate emu ya bulwadde bwa MVA (MVA-MERS-S).
