Makroscopy: pleurosis, pericarditis, okukaluba kw'amawuggwe n'obusa bw'amawuggwe
Ennyingo nnya ez'obunene bw'obulwadde bw'obusajja bw'akawuka ziyinza okulabibwa:
Obulwadde bw'ekika kya pneumonia: edema y'ekika kya pulmonary, hyperplasia ya pulmonary, pneumocytes ez'ekika kya atypical, obuzunguwazi obw'ekika kya interstitial obulimu lymphocyte infiltration n'okuteekebwa kw'amasimu agali mu multivalent giant cell
