Obulwadde ne kawuka byombi biyitibwa  coronavirus .
Mu kiseera ky'okusaasaana kw'akawuka mu Wuhan, China, akawuka n'obulwadde emirundi mingi baayitibwanga coronavirus ne coronavirus eya Wuhan.
Mu Jjanwali 2020, WHO yakubiriza okukozesa amannya ag'ebbali ag'endwadde 2019-nCov ne 2019-nCoV ag'obulwadde obw'amaanyi obw'okussa omukka ku kawuka ku kawuka n'endwadde, nga bagoberera ekiragiro kya 2015 ekikugira okukozesa ebifo mu mannya g'endwadde n'akawuka.
Amannya ag'obwannannyini COVID-19 ne SARS-CoV-2 gaakubibwa nga 11 Febwali 2020.
Olw'obunafu bw'ebikozesebwa mu by'okulabirira abantu, abakola ebintu ebimu bafulumya ebintu ebikozesebwa mu by'okulabirira abantu gamba nga ebiwayi n'ebitundu eby'ebikozesebwa mu by'okusaabaza.
Ng'ekyokulabirako, eddwaliro mu Italy bwe lyetaaga akatambi k'omukka mu bwangu era nga n'omuguzi tasobola kukasasula mu budde, ekitongole ekikola ku by'omu kitundu kyaddamu okukola n'okufulumya akatambi 100 mu kiro kimu.
Oluvannyuma lw'okusaasaana kw'ekirwadde kya COVID-19, endowooza ez'obulimba n'obufere ezikwata ku nsibuko y'obulwadde, obugazi bw'obulwadde, engeri y'obukuumi, obujjanjabi n'ebirala byabaddemu era ne bitandika okusaasaana ku mutimbagano.
Kirabika nti omuntu asobola okusaasaanya ekirwadde kino ku bisolo ebirala.
Okunoonyereza tekusobodde kufuna bukakafu bwa kusaasaanya kwa siriimu mu mbizzi, amatoola ne enkoko.
Tewali ddagala oba ddagala lya mukenenya liragiddwa okujjanjaba obulwadde buno.
Okunoonyereza okw'ensi yonna ku ddagala n'eddagala erigema COVID-19 mu kiseera kino kukolebwa ebitongole bya gavumenti, ebibinja by'abasomesa n'abanoonyereza mu by'amakolero.
Mu March, Ekitongole ky'obulamu eky'ensi yonna kyatandikawo okunoonyereza kw'eddagala lya SOLIDARITY okusobola okunoonyereza ku bujjanjabi bw'eddagala lino erirwanyisa akawuka erya 'anti-viral' eririna essuubi ekkulu ennyo.
Tewali ddagala lisobola kukozesebwa, naye ebitongole bingi birina eddagala erinaakozesebwa.
Ebyafaayo bya SARS-CoV byakozesebwa kubanga SARS-CoV ne SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikozesa lACE 2 okuyingira mu butoffaali bw'omuntu.
Enkola z'okukuzaamu essatu ze zikozesebwa mu kunoonyereza.
Ekisooka, bannasayansi bagezaako okukola eddagala erirwanyisa akawuka ako.
Okukozesa akawuka ako, ka kibeere nga tekakolera oba nga kafudde, kigendereddwa okuleetawo obuddukiro obw'amangu obw'omu mubiri gw'omuntu singa wabaawo omulundi omulala obulwadde bwa COVID-19.
Enteekateeka ey'okubiri, ey'eddagala eririmu eddagala erigema obulwadde erina ekigendererwa eky'okuteekawo eddagala eririmu obujjanjabi obukola ku bulwadde obuva ku bulwadde obuli mu ndwadde.
Ku SARS-CoV-2, okunoonyereza kuno kukwata ku protein S ey'ekika ekimu ekiyamba akawuka okuyingira mu ACE 2 receptor.
Enteekateeka ey'okusatu ye eya siriimu ez'omusaayi (DNA oba RNA, enkola empya ey'okukozesa eddagala ly'okusaasaanya).
Abasawo b'eddagala erya COVID-19 beetaaga okusooka okugezesebwa okulaba oba ddala lirinamu obujjanjabi obumala.
Omusaayi gw'omwana gulimu ekirungo ekitali kya bulabe ekikoppololwa okuva mu kawuka akaleeta obulwadde. Okukola eddagala nga lyesigama ku bulwadde, kyalagiddwa ng'ekizibu ekirala mu kukola eddagala erigema SARS-CoV-2, naye tekiriimu kkiriza.
Mu Apuli 2020, okunoonyereza okw'ekikemo okw'emirundi 300 kutegekeddwa.
Ebigezo musanvu byatunuulira eddagala erikkirizibwa erirwanyisa omusujja gw'ensiri, nga muno mwe mwali n'ebiri mu hydroxychloroquine oba chloroquine.
Obujjanjabi obukola ku siriimu bwe businga okukozesebwa mu China, ng'ebigezo bya Remdesivir mu mulundi ogwokusatu bikyali mu nsi ezitali zimu era nga biteekeddwa okufulumizibwa mu mwezi gwa Apuli.
Okunonyereza okw'amaanyi ku kukulaakulana kw'eddagala n'eddagala erirwanyisa COVID-19 kwaliwo mu Apuli 2020. Waliwo eddagala eritali lya kawuka eririko okussibwako essira mu kujjanjaba COVID-19, omuli remdesivir, chloroquine ne lhydroxychloroquine, lopinavir/ritonavir ne lopinavir/ritonavir nga zikwataganyizibwa ne linterferon beta.
Obujulizi obusookerwako bulaga nti remdesivir yali ya mugaso mu Maaki 2020.
Obulwadde bwa Remdesivir obusaasizi bwagenda bugenda bulungi mu balwadde.
Ebigezo by'eddagala eriyitibwa Chloroquine, eddagala erikozesebwa mu bujjanjabi bw'omusujja, lyayigirizibwa mu China mu February wa 2020, nga n'ebivuddeyo byabyo bya dda.
Kyokka, abamu basaba abeekenneenya eby'okunoonyereza bakole kinene.
Abakulembeze b'ebyobulamu mu China ne Korea bakubiriza okukozesa chloroquine.
Kyokka, ekitongole kya Wuhan Institute of Virology, wadde kikubiriza omusawo okulya gramu emu buli lunaku, kigamba nti emirundi ebiri omusawo ogwo gwa bulabe nnyo era gusobola n'okutta omuntu.
Nga 28 Ogwokusatu 2020, FDA yakkiriza okukozesa hydroxychloroquine ne chloroquine mu lukusa lwa bukebere olw'okukozesa abasawo abalwadde ba COVID-19. Ekitabo kya 7 eky'obulagirizi mu China era kitwaliramu interferon, ribavirin, oba lumiphenovir okulwanyisa COVID-19.
Ebiriwo ku ntandikwa biraga nti eddagala ly'eddagala lya ribavirine lyetaagisa okusobola okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu kisu.
Nitazoxanide yakubirizibwa okwongera okunoonyereza mu bifo by'omubiri oluvannyuma lw'okulaga nti erina obusobozi obutonotono obw'okuziyiza SARS-CoV-2.
Okunoonyereza ku chloroquine ne l-hydroxychloroquine nga kuliko oba nga tewali azithromycin, kuliko obuzibu obwali bulemesa abasawo okuteeka eddagala lino mu nkola nga tewali kunoonyereza okulala. Oseltamivir tegisobola kuziyiza SARS-CoV-2 mu mubiri era tewali kalonda yenna akwatibwako ku ngeri y'okujjanjabaamu COVID-19.
Okukubwa cytokine kiyinza okuba ekizibu mu mitendera egy'oluvannyuma eya COVID-19 ey'amaanyi.
Waliwo obukakafu obulaga nti hydroxychloroquine eyinza okuba n'ebikolwa eby'okuziyiza ekitta bantu. Tocilizumab yayingirirwa mu nkola ya bujjanjabi mu Kakiiko k'ebyobulamu mu China oluvannyuma lw'okunoonyereza okutono okwakolebwa.
Kigezesebwa mu Italy mu mitendera ebiri oluvannyuma lw'okulaga ebivudde mu bantu abalina obulwadde obw'amaanyi.
Okugatta n'okwekebeza omusaayi gwa ferritin mu musaayi okusobola okumanya cytokine, kirina okuziyiza embeera ng'ezo ezibaako abantu abamu abazirina okufa.
Enzijanjaba ya interleukin-6 receptor antagonist yakkirizibwa FDA okusinziira ku byakuyigirizibwa mu bantu ng'eyamba ku bulwadde bwa steroid-refractory cytokine relapse syndrome obuleetebwa enzijanjaba ya CAR T cell mu 2017.
Tewali bukakafu bwa mu ddagala obulaga nti tocilizumab eyamba ku bulwadde bwa SCR.
Okusaasaanya obuwuka obweggasibwa obwekikungo obuva mu bulwadde bw'abantu abawonye COVID-19 eri abantu ababwetaaga nga bwe bubeera enkola y'okuziyiza obulwadde nga tebasimbye mu ddagala.
Enkola eno yakeberwa ku SARS naye teyavaamu bibala.
Obulamu bw'omusaayi bw'ekimu ku bintu ebinaayamba okulwanyisa SARS-CoV-2 nga bafuba okubugumya.
Kyokka, enkola endala nga cytotoxicity eyeesigamye ku antibodies ne/ oba phagocytosis eyinza okuba nga esoboka.
Enkola endala ez'eddagala erirwanyisa endwadde nga tezikyakola, gamba ng'okozesa eddagala erirwanyisa endwadde erya monoclonal antibody, zikozesebwa.
Okufulumya seramu okuva mu bantu abawonye, nga kiva mu musaayi gw'abalwadde abawonye era nga gulimu obuziyiza obwekusifu eri akawuka kano, gusobola okwongerwako okusobola okusaasaanya eddagala lino mu bwangu.
